description:
Great news… we’ve given our app a whole new look! Now it’s easier than ever to outfit your #AEOSTYLE with the best AEO jeans, T’s, accessories and more. And for you Aerie girls, there is even more to celebrate as you can now shop your fave undies, bras and sleep, too! Share the love at #aerieREAL
	
• Buy AEO Gift Cards right from the app—and personalize a message to your recipient
• Now you can shop both AEO and Aerie in the app
• Shop our New Arrivals (before all your friends)
• Get a good look at our latest styles with full-screen photos
• Add your AEREWARDS card to Passbook so it's always with you
• Sign up for notifications so you know about our sales first (and other cool stuff)
• Check out in no time... since now you can enter your credit card with your camera
• Find your nearest AEO and Aerie stores, and find out if what you want is in stock

We can’t wait to hear what you think about our new app. Email us at AEOMobile@ae.com with your feedback. And be sure to keep your eye on the app for improvements, new features and more.
releaseNotes:
We've heard you loud and clear… and we've made a ton of changes to the app just for you. (And just in time for you to do a little holiday shopping, of course.)

• Aerie is in the app!
• Tabs in our navigation give you a whole new way to shop!
• Want to shop by trend? Now you can.
• Find great gifts for everyone on your list with the AEO Gift Guide.
• Bug fixes. Lots of them.

For you Aerie girls, both Aerie AND AEO brands are in the same app!

• The Aerie shop will allow all girls to shop their fave bras, undies, sleep and swim with new, easy navigation.
• Looking for gifts for your girls? Aerie gift guide is now added, too.
 
There's even more coming, too. And we love feedback, so be sure to speak up! Email us at AEOMobile@ae.com.
